comments: Fultz (ORL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Banchero (ORL) moves alongside Ivey's (DET) path and avoids making arm contact as he contests the driving shot attempt.
Duren (DET) initiates contact with Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm during the pursuit of the rebound and the contact affects his FOM.
Harris (ORL) is moving alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Bogdanovic (DET) goes to, not through, Harris' (ORL) space and marginal contact occurs as he releases away during the drive as Harris enhances the contact.
Wagner's (ORL) arm collapses to his body as he moves alongside Ivey's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs when they come together during the driving shot attempt.
Harris (ORL) reaches in and initiates contact with Bogdanovic's (DET) leg that affects his SQBR.
Harris (ORL) reaches in and initiates arm contact with Ivey (DET) that affects his SQBR as he attempts to make the pass.

Replay review of the out of bounds called on Wiseman (DET) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Banchero (ORL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds. DET retains possession.
Harris (ORL) reaches in and initiates illegal arm contact with Bogdanovic (DET) prior to dislodging the ball during the rip-through.
Stewart (DET) is moving alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Bogdanovic (DET) reaches in and brushes Banchero's (ORL) arm prior to his upward shooting motion and the contact is marginal.
Correctly called 24 second violation on Banchero (ORL).
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Wagner (ORL).
Ivey (DET) extends his leg outward and marginal contact occurs with Carter Jr. (ORL) as both players return to the floor, after Carter Jr. contests the jump shot attempt.
Livers (DET) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Banchero's (ORL) arm after the release.
Carter Jr. (ORL) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
